---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const imgBase = "https://identitysummitfiles.blob.core.windows.net/cis-images";
---

<Layout title="Cloud Identity Summit 2022">
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow">
        
        <div class="mb-12">
            <a href="/archive" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold transition bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                ← Back to Archive
            </a>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-8">
            Cloud Identity Summit 2022
        </h1>

        <div class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16 space-y-6">
            <p>The third Cloud Identity Summit took place on September 22, 2022. After two virtual conferences, we were able to offer the 3rd edition as a hybrid event and of course continue to offer it free of charge. The location was made available to us by adesso in Bonner Bogen.</p>
            <p>The conference consisted of two parts: in the morning we were able to offer two workshops and in the afternoon eight sessions were held on site and additionally streamed to participants all over the world. The subsequent roundtable with all experts rounded off the program.</p>
            <p>We would like to thank our speakers and our partners glueckkanja and yubico, without whom we would not have been able to offer the rich and informative program! We were very happy that we were finally able to meet in person and had a lot of fun together.</p>
        </div>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Impressions</h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <a data-fslightbox="gallery-2022" href={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0036.jpg`} class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all">
                    <img src={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0036.jpg`} alt="CIS 2022" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-video hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
                </a>
                <a data-fslightbox="gallery-2022" href={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0052.jpg`} class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all">
                    <img src={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0052.jpg`} alt="CIS 2022" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-video hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
                </a>
                <a data-fslightbox="gallery-2022" href={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0120.jpg`} class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all">
                    <img src={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0120.jpg`} alt="CIS 2022" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-video hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
                </a>
                <a data-fslightbox="gallery-2022" href={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0539.jpg`} class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all">
                    <img src={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0539.jpg`} alt="CIS 2022" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-video hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
                </a>
                <a data-fslightbox="gallery-2022" href={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0585.jpg`} class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all">
                    <img src={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0585.jpg`} alt="CIS 2022" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-video hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
                </a>
                <a data-fslightbox="gallery-2022" href={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0787.jpg`} class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all">
                    <img src={`${imgBase}/2022/10/Cloud_Identity_Summit_Vollmer0787.jpg`} alt="CIS 2022" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-video hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
                Photos by <a href="https://fotojetzt.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Tobias Vollmer</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">Agenda & Speakers</h2>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">9:30 am - 12:00 pm</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Hands on with decentralised identifiers and verifiable credentials</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Stefan van der Wiele</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">9:30 am - 12:00 pm</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Azure AD Security Testing with AADInternals</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400"><a href="https://o365blog.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Dr. Nestori Syynimaa</a></span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800/80 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 text-center col-span-full shadow-inner my-2">
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-1">12:00 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white text-lg tracking-wide">Lunch and Expo</strong>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-blue-900/20 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-800/50 text-center col-span-full mb-2">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-1">1:00 pm (10 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white text-lg">Welcome from the AzureBonn Orga Team</strong>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">1:10 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Azure AD Authentication Fundamentals</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400"><a href="https://gotoguy.blog/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Jan Vidar Elven</a></span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">1:10 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Azure RBAC, Access policies and other Azure Myths</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400"><a href="https://ericberg.de/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Eric Berg</a></span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">2:10 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">The state of Identity management in AKS</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">David Frappart</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">2:10 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Managed Identity for Hackers and Developers</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Sergey Chubarov</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800/80 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 text-center col-span-full shadow-inner my-2">
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-1">3:00 pm (30 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white text-lg tracking-wide">Coffee Break and Expo</strong>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">3:30 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Using Logic Apps to automate tasks in your AAD - and secure your Logic Apps</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400"><a href="https://chris-brumm.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Christopher Brumm</a></span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">3:30 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">AWS IAM - curse and blessing. 10 steps to follow to not end in a world of pain.</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400"><a href="https://cloud-right.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">David O'Brien</a></span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">4:30 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Azure Attack Paths</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400"><a href="https://cloudbrothers.info/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Fabian Bader</a></span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-2">4:30 pm (50 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white block mb-1 text-lg">Windows Hello for Business Hybrid Access: How Does It Work Under The Covers?</strong>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">Sander Berkouwer, Raymond Comvalius</span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800/80 p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50 text-center col-span-full shadow-inner mt-2">
                    <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm font-mono block mb-1">5:30 pm (60 min)</span>
                    <strong class="text-white text-lg tracking-wide">Roundtable & Raffle</strong>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/fslightbox/3.3.1/index.min.js" is:inline></script>
</Layout>